
* List of layers with spatial data
	- Set namespace
	- Set feature
	- Set Title
	- Set Abstract
	- Set Keywords
	- Toggle to require user to be logged in or not
	- Toggle to make service public or not 
	- Drop down to select layer type (Point, Line, Polygon)
	- List of meta keys for the post type with ability to toggle them on and off (except geometa keys?)

* Ability to publish a layer multiple times
	- Once with polygons once with points
	- Once that requires user to be logged in or not

* Map with list of layers and ability to toggle them on/off (on the map, for visualization purposes)

* WFS links
